<span STYLE="BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">
<span STYLE="WiDoWs: 2; orpHAns: 2; WorD-spACinG: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
【你有风险预案</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">think3</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">吗？】越是顺利，越是要考虑风险，越是正常，越是要考虑状况，预案永远是你需要提前思考准备的，所有的大楼，一根小小的火柴就能毁掉。风险没有不可能，一切灾难皆有可能。</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">1-</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">最坏的三种大危机，</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">2-</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">最容易出问题的三个环节，</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">3-</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">最可能出事的三个人。</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="WiDoWs: 2; orpHAns: 2; WorD-spACinG: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<font SIZE="3">&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="WiDoWs: 2; orpHAns: 2; WorD-spACinG: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<span STYLE="WiDoWs: 2; orpHAns: 2; WorD-spACinG: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<span><span STYLE="WiDoWs: 2; orpHAns: 2; WorD-spACinG: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<span STYLE="BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">
<span STYLE="WiDoWs: 2; orpHAns: 2; WorD-spACinG: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<span STYLE="WiDoWs: 2; orpHAns: 2; WorD-spACinG: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
【你刻骨铭心的是什么？】有想象的人都会把理想都写在脸上，真能实现的人是把壮志刻在心里。真正能产生刻骨铭心驱动的，是你用手摸着自己的心问自己，如果用十年做一件事，它是什么？</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="WiDoWs: 2; orpHAns: 2; WorD-spACinG: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<font SIZE="3">&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></P>
<p><span><span STYLE="BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">
【如何培育你的人脉】</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">1.</SPAN></SPAN> <span><span STYLE="BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">
学会与陌生人交流，迈出拉近距离第一步；</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">2.</SPAN></SPAN> <span><span STYLE="BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">
尊重别人是不够的，要帮助别人；</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">3.</SPAN></SPAN> <span><span STYLE="BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">
帮助别人是不够的，要付出多于回报；</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">4.</SPAN></SPAN> <span><span STYLE="BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">
在需要之前编织好人际网，接近能帮助你成功的贵人；</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">5.</SPAN></SPAN> <span><span STYLE="BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">
与有用或有潜力的人保持恰当的联系；</SPAN></SPAN><span><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">6.</SPAN></SPAN> <span><span STYLE="BACKGroUnD: white; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">
打造自己的智囊团，吸取拓展人脉的建议。</SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 10.5pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">&nbsp;</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="WiDoWs: 2; orpHAns: 2; WorD-spACinG: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
